    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1872-10-24T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1872-10-24T00:00:00-05:00" n="155" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d155">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">No. 16.</note>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. Fish</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                                Bancroft</persName>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1872-10-24">
                            <hi rend="italic">October</hi> 24, 1872.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Congratulations on the award. The President directs thanks, in which I
                            concur, for your able management of the case.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>FISH.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
